title: Ojou to Shinonome
sinopse:
The lady has fallen in love with her cool and smart servant, Shinonome!

Too bad Shinonome is actually very clueless, and completely unaware about the poor lady's feelings... What will happen to the little lady who's trying her best?

(Source: MU)

Included one-shot:
Volume 2: Ojou to Shinonome (pilot)
